# Card-audit (mtg-948 Part B): Drain Life — X damage + capped lifegain (scripted).
#
# Closed issue mtg-501 closed Drain Life as WORKING but carried NO scripted
# puzzle with semantic assertions (the pre-existing drain_life_cap.pzl /
# drain_life_creature_cap.pzl are golden-log-only with no [assertions],
# heuristic-driven). This audit puzzle SCRIPTS the cast and asserts BOTH the
# damage AND the (uncapped, here) life gain via semantic assertions.
#
# Drain Life is {X}{1}{B} sorcery: "deals X damage to any target. You gain life
# equal to the damage dealt, but not more than the [target's pre-damage
# characteristic]." Here X is funded by mana: P0 has 4 Swamps, paying {X}{1}{B}
# at X=2, so Drain Life deals 2 to P1 (a 20-life PLAYER), and P0 gains 2 (no cap
# triggers, since the player's pre-damage life 20 >= 2 damage). This exercises
# the common, uncapped path: damage AND equal life gain.
#
# Aspects exercised (issue mtg-501):
#   1. Parses + castable as a {X}{1}{B} sorcery (spell cast assertion).
#   2. X-paid damage to "any target" (here the opponent PLAYER): P1 20 -> 18.
#   3. Life gain equal to damage dealt (uncapped: 2 damage at a 20-life player
#      -> P0 gains exactly 2, 20 -> 22). The `life gained` event assertion checks
#      the gain explicitly.
#
# Scenario:
#   - P0: Drain Life in hand, 4 Swamps (-> X=2 + {1}{B}).
#   - P1: 20 life, no creatures.
#   - Script: P0 casts Drain Life at P1; deals 2 (P1 20->18); P0 gains 2 (20->22).

[metadata]
Name:Card Audit - Drain Life Deals X and Gains Equal Life
Goal:Win
Turns:1
Difficulty:Easy
Description:P0 scripts Drain Life ({X}{1}{B} sorcery) at the 20-life P1 with X=2 (4 Swamps). It deals 2 damage (P1 20->18) and P0 gains 2 life (20->22), uncapped since the player's pre-damage life exceeds the damage. Backs issue mtg-501 (DealDamageXPaid + GainLife equal to damage dealt).

[state]
turn=1
activeplayer=p0
activephase=MAIN1
p0life=20
p0hand=Drain Life
p0battlefield=Swamp;Swamp;Swamp;Swamp
p0library=Swamp;Swamp;Swamp;Swamp;Swamp

p1life=20
p1battlefield=
p1library=Mountain;Mountain;Mountain;Mountain;Mountain

[p0_script]
# Cast Drain Life at the opponent (P1). With 4 Swamps the engine pays {X}{1}{B}
# at X=2, dealing 2 damage and gaining 2 life.
cast Drain Life targeting p2

[assertions]
# The drain sorcery was actually cast.
spell cast Drain Life
# It dealt 2 damage to the 20-life opponent: P1 20 -> 18.
opponent life eq 18
# The caster (P0) gained exactly 2 life (equal to the damage dealt, uncapped):
# 20 -> 22.
life eq 22
# Explicit life-gain event: P0 gained at least 2 (the lifegain watcher fired).
life gained ge 2
